featured_reviews.review_id: The best Masjid in the surrounding areas following Quran n Hadeeth. Jumma bayan in Tamil, rarely in Urdu. Shaoor available for odd days and on Shawal 6 days,Arafat,  Aasura, and Ifthar available for Ramadan, Shawal, Arafat, Aasura. Tharavi prayers 8 Rakath and then bayan for one hour. Odd days extra Urdu bayan and whole night you can do any ibadath. Eclipse prayers conducted. Madarasa and free tuition also available. Rooms available for bachelors. For sisters islamic studies course is available which the batch starts after Ramadan every year.

featured_reviews.review_id:
Assalamu alaikum....

I feel proud to say to my muslim brothers that ,, those who looks for a Masjid nearby to Guindy railway station,, Nothing to worry.
There is a masjid  named as '''MASJID - E - BILAL  (R.A.Z)"" ,  a masjid which is very near to Guindy station.

A small Masjid with capacity of approximately 150 musallis.

DIRECTIONS:

1. From Guindy Railway station, take the path for going to Guindy Bus stand (from where buses goes to DLF, Porur, etc).

2. In the Main road,, you will find SIDCO Industrial estate ,, Opposite to which you will find '''SANGEETHA HOTEL""

3.  Next to Sangeetha hotel,, you will find a small street,  Go straight, until you get a curved LEFT turn,,

4.  You have reached the Destination.

Please explore the locality of the MASJID to large extent to our muslim brothers.

Jazakallah
